# SHACL spec §2.1.3.1 — sh:targetNode data graph.
# Source: https://www.w3.org/TR/shacl/#targetNode
# The shapes target ex:Alice only. ex:Alice has no ex:name → 1 violation.
# ex:Bob also has no ex:name but is not targeted → no violation for Bob.
PREFIX ex: <http://example.com/ns#>

ex:Alice a ex:Person .
ex:Bob a ex:Person ; ex:name "Bob" .
